com.ephesoft.dcma.regexpp.service

Interface RegexService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RegexServiceImpl

    public interface RegexService
    This service is used to read Key Value Pattern from an image file and writes the value, coordinates and confidence score in page level Fields inside batch.xml. Confidence score is decided on the basis of key value i.e. 100 if key and value is found and 0 if not found.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ephesoft
    See Also:
    com.ephesoft.dcma.barcode.service.RegexServiceImpl
